sections.description:
Wallet is your personal cabinet where you can perform and track your transactions, such as:
- Buying CMN tokens;
- Exchanging of community Points into CMN tokens and vice versa;
- Sending Points to your friends;
- Tracking the balance of Points of each community you are subscribed to;
- Tracking the history of transactions and rewards;
Also, you can always see the equity value of your account in USD or CMN tokens. It’s the total value of all your community Points, as well as the CMN tokens that you hold.

